CWE-200:
$The translate_desc function in drivers/vhost/vhost.c in the Linux kernel before 3.7 does not properly handle cross-region descriptors, which allows guest OS users to obtain host OS privileges by leveraging KVM guest OS privileges.$Per https://access.redhat.com/security/cve/CVE-2013-0311
"This issue did affect the version of Linux kernel as shipped with Red Hat Enterprise Linux 6."$
